<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٩١⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٤٨٣٥ -<span class="c5"> عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ قَالَ:</span> أَخْبَرَنَا مَعْمَرٌ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ ابْنِ شُبْرُمَةَ قَالَ:</span> سَأَلْتُهُ عَنِ الْبَيْعِ، أَيَقْطَعُ الْإِجَارَةَ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«نَعَمْ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>